We will offer them active monitoring, and if the disease starts to progress, we will start treatment.
Increasingly, we accurately determine the criteria for deciding who should or should not undergo treatment.
So, I would still recommend taking the test.
But it is also important to consult your doctor to determine whether or not you need to pass this test.
